2006-11-20 Version 2.0 
	Differences with respect to 1.0:
		- New example figure with subfigures
		- Explanation of bibtex a bit expanded
		- Significant changes in atlasphysics.sty:
			- use of xspace.sty to get spacing right
			- change of names of various commands in order to
        		  minimize use of 1- and 2-letter commands
			- some new commands
	Please read the appendix of atlaspaper.tex to get a new list.
